  "title": "Service Sales Executive (After Sales) -  Training Provided  [0580]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Basic Salary: $2,500 - $2,800 + Comm</li><li>Mon – Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm</li><li>Office Location: Ubi</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Build and maintain good relations and close contact with clients, especially decision makers and stay informed of any plans for additional entrance or enhancement to existing entrances</li><li>Conduct market research and feasibility studies to propose new accessories for automated entrance – Such may include local norms/regulations studies</li><li>3rd party entrance market penetration: Develop and adopt strategies for all 3rd party equipment with the aim of converting the equipment to the company type</li><li>Manage and negotiate all contracts secured and ensure terms are neutral and not unfavourable</li><li>Risk manages all contract terms and conditions</li><li>Achieving Sales targets (figures) allocated.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree Holder of engineering or business disciplines</li><li>Preferably with relevant technical background</li><li>PC Literate & Proficiency is MS office</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
